    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about \"healing\" anymore. that feels like a joke. there's nothing left to reclaim. the person who could have been happy, who actually wanted things... they're gone. i'm just performing the motions of existing. it's like being buried alive in my own skin.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
